latestIgtvVideos.title: #boyslockerroom My request to the “new generation”
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Sorry for not bringing this up before. 🙏

Rapes can be stopped at any early stage.
This is what I really want
Am not saying this is right but it’s not their fault totally, it’s the friends and the environment which shape your mind and they think it’s cool in this new generation. Slut shaming and characterising women and giving them titles is an easy task today. Suddenly all of us have become “cool” and we are okay with things which were not acceptable before. We want to bring in change. But as elder brothers/sisters/parents or friends we need to tell them that sharing something which is personal to someone is not COOL.
.
.
#boislockerroom #boysroom #lockerroom #lockeroom
